@LingoCross.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5093

### Sağlık kontrolü
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Kayıt (öğretmen)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com",
  "password": "Sifre1234!",
  "displayName": "Örnek Öğretmen",
  "role": 1
}

### Giriş
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com",
  "password": "Sifre1234!"
}

### Token yenileme
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<refresh-token>"
}

### Çıkış
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<refresh-token>"
}

### Şifremi unuttum (her zaman 200)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com"
}

### Şifre sıfırlama (6 haneli kod e-postadan; dev'de log'a yazılır)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ogretmen@example.com",
  "code": "123456",
  "newPassword": "YeniSifre9!"
}

### Profilim (Bearer access token gerekir)
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

###

# ===== M3: Enrollment =====

### Öğretmen davet kodu (yoksa üretir) — Teacher
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teachers/me/invite-code
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Öğretmen davet kodunu yenile — Teacher
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teachers/me/invite-code/regenerate
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Öğrenci koddan katıl (idempotent, doğrudan Active) — Student
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments/join
Authorization: Bearer <student-access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ABCD2345"
}

### Eşleşmelerim (öğretmen → öğrenciler, öğrenci → öğretmenler)
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### (Pending akışı için) Eşleşmeyi onayla — Teacher
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments/<enrollment-id>/accept
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Öğrenci olarak görünür dersler (enrolled + published) — Student
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/lessons
Authorization: Bearer <student-access-token>

###

### ───────── F4.3: Adlandırılmış Sınıflar ─────────

### Sınıf oluştur (davet kodu üretilir) — Teacher
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "9A"
}

### Sınıflarım (arşivlenmemiş, studentCount ile) — Teacher
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Sınıf detayı (aktif üyelerle) — Teacher
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/<class-id>
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Sınıf adını güncelle — Teacher
PUT {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/<class-id>
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "9A (Sabah)"
}

### Sınıfı arşivle — Teacher
DELETE {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/<class-id>
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Sınıf davet kodu (yoksa üretir) — Teacher
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/<class-id>/invite-code
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Sınıf davet kodunu yenile — Teacher
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/<class-id>/invite-code/regenerate
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Sınıftan öğrenci çıkar — Teacher
DELETE {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/<class-id>/students/<student-id>
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### Sınıflarım (öğrenci) — Student
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/me
Authorization: Bearer <student-access-token>

### Sınıfa koddan katıl (idempotent) — Student
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/classes/join
Authorization: Bearer <student-access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ABCD2345"
}

### Oyunu sınıflara ata (SET semantiği) — Teacher
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/games/<game-id>/assignments
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classIds": ["<class-id-1>", "<class-id-2>"]
}

### Oyunun atandığı sınıflar — Teacher
GET {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/games/<game-id>/assignments
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>

### OCR ham metnini Claude ile zenginleştir — Teacher
### (Anthropic__ApiKey yoksa 503 döner; mobil yerel ayrıştırmaya düşer)
POST {{LingoCross.Api_HostAddress}}/api/ocr/enrich
Authorization: Bearer <teacher-access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rawText": "happy mutlu\nsad uzgun\nbook kitap",
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "targetLanguage": "tr"
}

###
